ZH: 1. 他答应我明天帮我搬家。
EN: He promised to help me move tomorrow.
ZH: 2. 她答应参加我的生日派对。
EN: She agreed to attend my birthday party.
ZH: 3. 我父母答应我买一只小狗。
EN: My parents promised to buy me a puppy.
ZH: 4. 我们不能答应这个不公平的要求。
EN: We cannot agree to this unfair demand.
ZH: 5. 他们答应在周末一起出去玩。
EN: They agreed to go out together on the weekend.
ZH: 6. 她答应了我的请求帮我改正错误。
EN: She agreed to my request to help me correct the mistake.
ZH: 7. 我答应给他寄明信片。
EN: I promised to send him a postcard.
ZH: 8. 请你答应我不要告诉别人。
EN: Please promise me not to tell anyone.
ZH: 9. 他答应帮我练习华佗拳。
EN: He agreed to help me practice Huatuquan.
ZH: 10. 他们答应了我年底提升我的薪水。
EN: They promised to increase my salary at the end of the year.
ZH: 11. 她答应了我的道歉并原谅了我。
EN: She accepted my apology and forgave me.
ZH: 12. 我请你答应我以后不再迟到。
EN: I ask you to promise me that you won't be late again.
ZH: 13. 他答应过来看望我住院的爷爷。
EN: He promised to visit my hospitalized grandfather.
ZH: 14. 我们不能答应那么快完成这个项目。
EN: We cannot agree to complete this project so quickly.
ZH: 15. 他们答应帮助受困的移民。
EN: They agreed to assist the stranded immigrants.
ZH: 16. 请你答应我好好休息一下。
EN: Please promise me to take a good rest.
ZH: 17. 我不答应你的荒谬要求。
EN: I won't agree to your ridiculous demand.
ZH: 18. 她答应了嫁给那个男人。
EN: She agreed to marry that man.
ZH: 19. 他答应向我借钱。
EN: He promised to lend me money.
ZH: 20. 请你答应我不要打扰我写作业。
EN: Please promise me not to disturb me while I'm doing my homework.
